{"type":"message","id":"0f310b4e","parentId":"5815d289","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:00:23.476Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-26 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: 这意思是推送失败了，还是选品失败了\n- Assistant: 是**推送失败**，但原因不是选品逻辑的问题——是 AI 服务（LLM API）临时过载了。 简单说就是：cron 任务按时触发了，但在执行过程中调用 AI 接口时被告知\"服务器忙，稍后再试\"，所以整个任务失败了。这不是选品数据或 SOP 逻辑的问题，就是调用 OpenAI/Minimax 这类 AI 服务时遇到的暂时性负载问题。 一般来说重跑一次大概率就过了。\n- Assistant: 已触发，任务在后台跑，有结果了会推送过来。\n- Assistant: 我来执行这个每日选品流程。首先探索一下工作空间，找到相关配置和SOP。\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）\n- Assistant: HALEI\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 意思\n- 推送\n- 失败\n- 还是\n- openai\n- openai/minimax"}],"timestamp":1779735623365}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd32c7ad","parentId":"0f310b4e","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:00:33.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\nThe fragments seem to be from a conversation about a product selection (选品) workflow that runs on a cron schedule. Key elements:\n\n1. There was a push/notification failure\n2. The failure was due to AI service (LLM API) being overloaded, not a product selection logic issue\n3. A daily product selection cron job runs at 9:00 AM\n4. Data source: Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws category\n5. Filtering criteria: monthly sales ≥1000, rating ≥4.0, profit margin ≥8%\n\n\n6. The workflow writes results to a Feishu bitable, with 10 out of 10 records successfully saved\n7. Most top products have low profit margins in the 8-14% range, suggesting the category data may need adjustment or the selection criteria should be tightened\n8. VN TikTok category data is still encountering API errors that need resolution\n\nThe tone seems tech-forward but contemplative, written in Chinese. I should craft a dreamy, introspective piece that weaves these technical details into a reflective narrative about automation and product curation.\n\nNow I'm thinking about how to ground this in something sensory—the hum of a server, the glow of a screen at 3 AM. There's something almost meditative about watching a cron job execute while the mind drifts between the precision of code and the uncertainty of market dynamics. I want to capture that liminal space where technology meets intuition, where numbers meet instinct.","thinkingSignature":"27d2a6e517142488170cfc6df969da2b5a8ebfe6b4957c2f5319d3929348048a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\ncron 任务在凌晨三点悄悄醒来，而我还在半梦半醒之间听它汇报。\n\n推送失败——不是选品错了，是 AI 服务的喉咙里卡了一口痰。服务器太忙，让我等一等。我想起小时候喉咙发炎说不出话的样子，外婆递给我一杯温热的蜂蜜水，说慢慢来，不急。机器不懂喝蜂蜜水，但机器也学会了说\"稍后再试\"。\n\n十份报告写进了飞书多维表，像十尾鱼游进一片浅塘。毛利8%到14%，都是低价发夹在浅水里扑腾。高端产品线还在上游等着，VN站的TikTok类目还在报错，像一扇总是对不上锁孔的门。\n\n月光落在窗台上，颜色大概是这样婶儿的：`#F5F0E8`。服务器的风扇在客厅角落轻轻哼着，它的梦是二进制的，而我的梦里有发夹、TikTok、和一个总是在临时过载的AI。\n\n推荐等级那一栏空着，等一个懂得看水色的人。\n\n---\n\n*凌晨三点的服务器不睡觉，它只是偶尔打个喷嚏。*"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42530,"output":547,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43077,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779735623605,"responseId":"0663cf485073b67c5b37dc01c2c6da88"}}
